くなるような動画を作りつづけたい！\n\n全部の動画を見なくてもいいです。\nたまに動画を見てくれるだけでも、本当に嬉しいです。\n好きな時に、ふらっと動画を見にきてください。\n\n\nドズル社は新しいチャレンジをして、アップデートします。\n将来どんなことができるか、ワクワクです。\n一緒にドズル社の変化を楽しみながら、人生というゲームを楽しみましょう！\n\n\nドズルより\n\nBGM courtesy of https://www.epidemicsound.com/\n\n＃ドズル社 #マイクラ #マインクラフト", "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/92YqHVKmyLs/maxresdefault_live.webp", "manifest_urls": ["https://manifest.googlevideo.com/api/manifest/hls_playlist/expire/1781451526/ei/pnYuauWxMP2mvcAPguPU8Q0/ip/125.102.248.226/id/92YqHVKmyLs.0/itag/91/source/yt_premiere_broadcast/requiressl/yes/ratebypass/yes/live/1/sgoap/gir%3Dyes%3Bitag%3D139/sgovp/gir%3Dyes%3Bitag%3D160/rqh/1/hls_chunk_host/rr4---sn-oguesn6d.googlevideo.com/xpc/EgVo2aDSNQ%3D%3D/bui/ARmQxEXuCy_2nFrYCxnjq1DT9WNb-fSAUo4JRWE8I1Th0k_Y6QAZmoULR05fe-Tv8_b2_ZcV-TxOmWAw/spc/SQ-umtWrDX-vjdjYqoaWkjhNhQafCUrmVboeVOdDmTiv8352Yg/vprv/1/reg/0/playlist_type/DVR/hcs/sd/initcwndbps/4120000/met/1781429927,/mh/qU/mm/44/mn/sn-oguesn6d/ms/lva/mv/m/mvi/4/pl/21/rms/lva,lva/smhost/rr3---sn-oguesnd7.googlevideo.com/dover/11/pacing/0/keepalive/yes/fexp/51565115,51565682/mt/1781429543/sparams/expire,ei,ip,id,itag,source,requiressl,ratebypass,live,sgoap,sgovp,rqh,xpc,bui,spc,vprv,reg,playlist_type/sig/AHEqNM4wRgIhAIvUZuBr7H-K6XcCniKG4WdWhtb3O-cRF0WDTiUJfmY1AiEAlrB8ry7GTvJVULI7XjswVIASxcucgkRYs0bf9XtfX0w%3D/lsparams/hls_chunk_host,hcs,initcwndbps,met,mh,mm,mn,ms,mv,mvi,pl,rms,smhost/lsig/APaTxxMwRAIgfidp0iCq8NSJHZIw-iVsA1BzBfBBqOJw2BTt0XDpqa0CIGzUj4vAU9c5gkebqAlMbtdnhowHexzA5w6IM8rJXMw4/playlist/index.m3u8", "https://manifest.googlevideo.com/api/manifest/hls_playlist/expire/1781451526/ei/pnYuauWxMP2mvcAPguPU8Q0/ip/125.102.248.226/id/92YqHVKmyLs.0/itag/92/source/yt_premiere_broadcast/requiressl/yes/ratebypass/yes/live/1/sgoap/gir%3Dyes%3Bitag%3D139/sgovp/gir%3Dyes%3Bitag%3D133/rqh/1/hls_chunk_host/rr4---sn-oguesn6d.googlevideo.com/xpc/EgVo2aDSNQ%3D%3D/bui/ARmQxEXuCy_2nFrYCxnjq1DT9WNb-fSAUo4JRWE8I1Th0k_Y6QAZmoULR05fe-Tv8_b2_ZcV-TxOmWAw/spc/SQ-umtWrDX-vjdjYqoaWkjhNhQ